The paper deals with mechanism design, which is a subfield of game theory (cs.GT). It also involves optimization problems and algorithms (cs.DS), as well as incentive compatibility and Bayesian settings (cs.AI). The paper specifically focuses on welfare maximization (cs.EC) and the complexity of black-box reductions (cs.IT).
